{% extends 'layout.njk' %}

{% set title = 'About' %}

{% block mainContent %}
  <article class="message">
    <div class="message-body">
      Draft My CV is a tool for anyone currently going through the process of 
      <strong>job hunting</strong>. I created this site as a way to quickly create a
      great CV (or resume) to cut out all the hours I used to spend trying to put together
      a perfect CV. Simply enter your details, hit <strong>Submit</strong> and your CV will
      be ready to download as either a Word document or a PDF, the most compatible formats
      for submitting alongside a job application. Job hunting is far from a fun process, so
      I hope this makes your life a little easier... Good luck!
    </div>
  </article>
{% endblock mainContent %}